divs: Sighting Detailsok i am a archery hunter and installed several trail cams. on one i captured a photo of something that i never seen before, you would have to see it to believe. I saved the sd card out of the trail cam. I've also showed it to several people and nobody has a clue what it might be. Sorry can not attach photo. If interested call my cell phone that is listed above.
Summary: i have a picture of an unknown person with a green face big black eyes holding something bright.
